  "title": "Private Chat — Doing the Safety Dance in the Lower Middle Market",
  "body": "<html><body><div class=\"node__content\"> <section class=\"detail-page-head full-width-block\"><div class=\"container medium\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-12\"> <small>Deerpath Capital- <span class=\"field field--name-created field--type-created field--label-hidden\"><time class=\"datetime\" datetime=\"2026-03-17T08:29:11+00:00\" title=\"Tuesday, March 17, 2026 - 08:29\">Tue, 03/17/2026 - 08:29</time></span></small><h1><span class=\"field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden\">Private Chat — Doing the Safety Dance in the Lower Middle Market</span></h1></div></div></div> </section> <section class=\"detail-page additional-height\"><div class=\"container medium\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-8-lg\"><div class=\"feature-image-visability\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-banner field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__item\"><article class=\"media media--type-image media--view-mode-default insurance-library-image\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-visually_hidden\"><div class=\"field__label visually-hidden\">Image</div><div class=\"field__item\"> <img alt=\"DeerpathFeaturedPodcast\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid\" data-src=\"/sites/default/files/2026-03/DeerpathFeaturedPodcast.jpg\" height=\"422\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2026-03/DeerpathFeaturedPodcast.jpg\" width=\"1004\"/></div></div> </article></div></div><div class=\"audio-player\"></div><p>Recent headlines suggest the private credit market is beginning to crumble; however, the asset class isn't a monolith. Look further downmarket, and a far more resilient story emerges. In this episode of Cloud 9fin, US private credit deputy editor Shubham Saharan is joined by Natalie Garcia, Deerpath's head of underwriting, as well as Reed Van Gorden, Deerpath’s head of origination, to discuss how the lower middle market is staying steady despite industry headwinds. <br/><br/></p><p><a class=\"btn btn-tritory\" href=\"/deerpath-capital\">Read More from Deerpath Capital</a></p><div class=\"avalible-pods\"><div class=\"block block-block-content block-block-content9a03abe3-6e62-4857-9ccf-a8978d7294f7\" id=\"block-podcastisavailableon\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-link-with-image field--type-entity-reference-revisions field--label-hidden field__items\"><div class=\"field__item\"><h3>The InsuranceAUM.com podcast is available on</h3><div class=\"btns-wrapper\"> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/6WIbsYrL1BXuJMPsZXSk8R\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2023-08/btn2.png\" width=\"200px\"/></a> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/insuranceaum-com/id1500643401\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2023-08/btn3.png\" width=\"200px\"/></a> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/InsuranceAUM-com/dp/B08K57V1D6\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2025-03/Frame%20366%20%281%29.png\" width=\"200px\"/></a> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@InsuranceAUMCommunity\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2025-03/frame_366%20%281%29%20%281%29.png\" width=\"200px\"/></a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"col-4-lg\"><div class=\"addtoany-social-icons mb-3\"><div class=\"addtoany-social-icons mb-3\"><h4>Share this post</h4> <span class=\"a2a_kit a2a_kit_size_32 addtoany_list d-flex gap-2 justify-content-start\" data-a2a-title=\"Private Chat — Doing the Safety Dance in the Lower Middle Market\" data-a2a-url=\"https://insuranceaum.com/private-chat-doing-the-safety-dance-in-the-lower-middle-market\"><a class=\"a2a_button_linkedin\"></a><a class=\"a2a_button_x\"></a><a class=\"a2a_button_facebook\"></a><a class=\"a2a_button_email\"></a><a class=\"a2a_button_print\"></a></span></div